      • isEnabled

        public boolean isEnabled()
        Gets the pack200 enabled configuration value.
        Please note: Setting this value to true requires SDK 5.0 or greater.
        Returns:
        true if pack200 compression of jar resources is enabled, false otherwise.

      • getPassFiles

        public List<String> getPassFiles()
        Gets the files within jar archive to be passed without pack200 compression.
        If file ends with a /, all files in the directory are passed through without packing.
        The same functionality as achievable by: 
         pack200 --pass-file= file, -P file
        Returns:
        the files to be passed without pack200 compression.
